{"type":null,"faqId":37068,"title":"使用蓝牙耳机通话时如何调节音量？在通话过程中上下滑动，不能调节通话音量怎么办？蓝牙耳机通话声音小怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-family:宋体;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>1、在使用蓝牙耳机通话过程中，黑屏状态下，用手指上下在耳机屏幕滑动，即可调节蓝牙耳机音量大小，你也可以通过手机的音量按键来调节音量。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、当不能调节音量时：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>（1）请保持您的手机和B2在3-5m之内且没有大的物体遮挡和隔离</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>（2）检查手机音量是否调节至最大</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、蓝牙通话声音小时：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>（1）</span><span class=\"s1\">请将固件升级到最新版本，新版本针对蓝牙通话声音小的问题有优化</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>（2）如升级后问题仍无解决，请上升至CSE。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":209,"faqType":"连接与配对","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2232","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Connection-Paring","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750141000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":180,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,音量调节,声音小","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}